      "y": 1330,
      "width": 1100,
      "height": 20,
      "text": "ADR-note: Node.ID is SHA-1 of canonical FQN (\"pkg/path#Type.Method\"). Stable across re-analysis \u2192 Cytoscape reuses positions (FR-11, FR-26).",
      "originalText": "ADR-note: Node.ID is SHA-1 of canonical FQN (\"pkg/path#Type.Method\"). Stable across re-analysis \u2192 Cytoscape reuses positions (FR-11, FR-26).",
