      "x": 72,
      "y": 1355,
      "width": 1100,
      "height": 20,
      "text": "Edge.ID is SHA-1 of (Source|Target|Kind). Weight is a hint only (e.g. how many call-sites) \u2014 absence of Weight should never break rendering.",
